---
title: Patatas Bravas Salad with Spicy Aioli, Almonds, and Feta
description: Patatas bravas is one of Spain’s most beloved late-night snacks, and we totally understand why. It consists of crispy fried potatoes drizzled with a warm and slightly spicy aioli sauce (excuse us while we drool over how delicious that sounds). Our chefs, Freida and Nate, transformed it into a meal by adding peppery arugula, juicy tomatoes, and creamy feta. Olé!
